{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/1.png?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you are thalassophobic, Achluophobic, claustrophobic, batophobic, or even teratophobic, you will be in an underwater <strong>nightmare</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/2.png?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in the depths of Gornak and try to repair old underwater facilities <strong>to help the union</strong> and serve your sentence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/dive_and_repent.gif?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/3.png?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will undoubtedly encounter the local fauna... <i>more or less dangerous</i>, but if you pray to Stiska you might find your redemption.. <strong>And even more in our magnificent submarine at the cutting edge of gornak technology !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/fish.gif?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/4.png?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To give you every chance of survival and success, you will come along your companions and pray to not be the last one <strong>drowning </strong>in these deadly waters. However, if you are alone, the Gornacian metallurgical union will help you as best as it can to prevent your death or worse.. The loss of a submarine</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/ezgif-5-6e09e06ea0.gif?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/5.png?t=1737500307\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737500307","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/page.bg.jpg?t=1737500307","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/9e40a7b61d8e5cb1818b31d8b36209f595d76ca9/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737500307","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/9e40a7b61d8e5cb1818b31d8b36209f595d76ca9/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737500307","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"The game's atmosphere is realistic, and the player's character can die by decapitation, dismemberment or drowning. Medical drugs can also be used recklessly by the player."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/1.png?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you are thalassophobic, Achluophobic, claustrophobic, batophobic, or even teratophobic, you will be in an underwater <strong>nightmare</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/2.png?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in the depths of Gornak and try to repair old underwater facilities <strong>to help the union</strong> and serve your sentence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/dive_and_repent.gif?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/3.png?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will undoubtedly encounter the local fauna... <i>more or less dangerous</i>, but if you pray to Stiska you might find your redemption.. <strong>And even more in our magnificent submarine at the cutting edge of gornak technology !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/fish.gif?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/4.png?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To give you every chance of survival and success, you will come along your companions and pray to not be the last one <strong>drowning </strong>in these deadly waters. However, if you are alone, the Gornacian metallurgical union will help you as best as it can to prevent your death or worse.. The loss of a submarine</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/ezgif-5-6e09e06ea0.gif?t=1737500307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995260/extras/5.png?t=1737500307\" /></p>","developers":["Nerra Tolsto\u00ef","FLaV"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":